Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:11.51,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一起来 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:14.48,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}许愿吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:18.51,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握的手儿是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:23.96,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我永远也不会松开
